Mix all the marinade ingredients together, rub well into the chicken and leave in the fridge for 1 hour.Preheat the oven to 200C/180C Fan/Gas 6.Put the chicken in a roasting tin, drizzle with the olive oil and scatter the sesame seeds over. Roast in the oven for 30 minutes or until cooked through. (To check the chicken is cooked, pierce at the thickest part of the thigh - the juices should run clear.)